T02TD2813E:167b-0: @167b * // thugs rje chen po gtsug tor nas byung ba'i rgyal po la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD2813E:167b-1: mtshan mar 'dzin pa'i skye bo ldongs pa yang //
T02TD2813E:167b-2: gang gis shes rab thugs rje 'bar ba yis //
T02TD2813E:167b-3: mi gtong rtag tu spyi gtsug rtsa mchog rtser //
T02TD2813E:167b-4: brtan bzhugs bdag gir mdzad pa dgongs grub shog /
T02TD2813E:167b-5: mi ni ring nas dad dang mngon 'dod yod //
T02TD2813E:167b-6: de la drang srong nam yang mi ring ste //
T02TD2813E:167b-7: thag ring mtsho nang padma skyes pa yang //
T02TD2813E:167b-8: bung ba nags na gnas pa nyin rer brtul //
T02TD2813E:167b-9: 'di na tshangs sogs grags chen mthu can yang //
T02TD2813E:167b-10: na rgas skye 'chi srid pa'i dgra tshogs las //
T02TD2813E:168a-0: rgyal bar ma gyur yang ma spangs @168a * //
T02TD2813E:168a-2: nus pa bdag la ci zhig bde ba yis //
T02TD2813E:168a-3: sa gsum dbang phyug 'jig rten skyob nyid 'dir //
T02TD2813E:168a-4: mchog dman bar ma'i yid can skal rim bzhin //
T02TD2813E:168a-5: snying dbus spyi gtsug ring nas skyob dam bcas //
T02TD2813E:168a-6: de bzhin skyabs 'dod gtsug tor cho ga bsam //
T02TD2813E:168a-7: dkyil 'khor bstan bcas mig phab ste //
T02TD2813E:168a-8: smyug ma lta bu'i tshigs rgyun gyis //
T02TD2813E:168a-9: sgo gnyis nas ni dbugs bzlog la //
T02TD2813E:168a-10: rtsa mchog rtser ni thugs dbang lha //
T02TD2813E:168a-11: rta mchog lam ni sdong bus te //
T02TD2813E:168a-13: spyi gtsug 'dab ma bye bas te //
T02TD2813E:168a-14: de steng mtho gang 'phags pa lha //
T02TD2813E:168a-15: lnga ldan yal ga dbus 'dab la //
T02TD2813E:168a-17: rtsa skyob rlung skyob thig le skyob //
T02TD2813E:168a-19: hr'i: yig snying ga las 'ongs sa bon dang //
T02TD2813E:168a-20: ri dbang nas bskyod ye shes lha //
T02TD2813E:168a-21: 'dus gyur bde gshegs bzhir bcas yum //
T02TD2813E:168a-22: sgrub pa pos ni rnam par bsgom //
T02TD2813E:168a-23: 'od dang thig le mnyam par gzhag /
T02TD2813E:168a-24: rang gnas snyoms par 'jug pa dang //
T02TD2813E:168a-26: zhi ba nyid dang 'od gsal rtag / thog ma bar dang mthar rim bzhin //
T02TD2813E:168a-27: smin mtshams tshangs sgo nam mkha' yi //
T02TD2813E:168a-29: nyid kyi sngon du dam bcas pa'o //
T02TD2813E:168a-30: gang dag rnam bar mi g-yeng bas //
T02TD2813E:168a-31: thun gsum du ni rtag tu dran //
T02TD2813E:168a-32: snying rje chen pos kun spyod pa //
T02TD2813E:168a-33: kha na ma tho med 'grub rgyu //
T02TD2813E:168a-34: padmo'i sdong bu can gyi sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
